\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 The five stories, conceived as a sort of philosophical and anthropological reconstruction of architecture, first appeared, as texts, images and storyboard, on the pages of "Casabella" magazine in 1972 and 1973. \
\
Superstudio felt this was a new way of expanding ideas beyond architecture.
